name: Jad
body:
### Welcome to Jad.
Jad is a network anomaly detection library for Java.
This project is under construction. The first release is scheduled for May 2013.
Feel free to visit our wiki and documentation pages for more info about Jad.

### Authors and Contributors
Denis Hock (@DenisHock).
